<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Citas Medicas</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <style>
        body {
            background: linear-gradient(120deg, #e0f6fc, #cfdef3);
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 450px;
            margin: 80px auto;
            background: #fff;
            border-radius: 16px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(44, 62, 80, 0.15);
            padding: 40px 32px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .logo {
            width: 80px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        h1 {
            color: #2d3e50;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        p {
            color: #4a6572;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .btn-group {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 16px;
            align-items: center;
        }
        .main-btn {
            background: #1976d2;
            color: #fff;
            border: none;
            padding: 14px 36px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 1.1em;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background 0.2s;
            text-decoration: none;
            display: inline-block;
            width: 80%;
            max-width: 250px;
        }
        .main-btn:hover {
            background: #1565c0;
        }
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .container {
                padding: 24px 8px;
            }
            .main-btn {
                width: 100%;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <img src="https://img.icons8.com/ios-filled/100/1976d2/doctor-male.png" alt="Medical Logo" class="logo"/>
        <h1>Bienvenido a citas medicas!!</h1>
        <p>
            Programe, gestione y haga seguimiento de sus citas médicas fácilmente. <br>
            Su salud, organizada y accesible.
            
        </p>
        <div class="btn-group">
            <a href="auth/login" class="main-btn">Iniciar sesión</a>
            <a href="auth/crearCuenta" class="main-btn">Crear cuenta</a>
            <a href="citas/agendarCita" class="main-btn">Agendar cita</a>
            <a href="citas/consultarCitas" class="main-btn">Consultar citas</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
